Package commands

Interface Command

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddCommand, AscendingCommand, AscendingHeightCommand, ClearCommand, ExitCommand, FilterLocationCommand, HelpCommand, InfoCommand, RemoveCommand, RemoveGreaterCommand, RemoveLessCommand, RunScriptCommand, SaveCommand, ShowCommand, ShuffleCommand, UpdateCommand
public interface Command
Brief:
Interface for all of the commands. If you want to write one, add it to the CommandRegestry.
